fields.name: CHESTERFIELD Sofa group 3-seater+2-seater+Armchair
fields.description: Chesterfield is a sofa group with a trendy appearance in a classic British style. Style the living room by investing in a timeless sofa group that offers both 2-seater, 3-seater and a mammoth armchair in one and the same package. The furniture has a pleasant, upholstered seat that guarantees maximum comfort and the button-studded design is a stylish hit that is rounded off by the beautifully shaped legs that support the furniture. This soffa group is available online and in our showroom

fields.name: Dynir 4-seat corner sofa-bed
fields.description: Dynir sofa bed in a modern style and mammoth design with generous dimensions and good sitting comfort. The sofa's open layout invites you to a comfortable sofa suspension that allows you to spread out properly. Do you get unexpected overnight guests? - No problem, make a bed for the guests in Dynir and they will sleep well all night.. This bed soffa is available online and in our showroom

fields.name: EMRIK 2,5-sits Soffa Bonded Leather
fields.description: Create a comfortable and stylish place for the whole family with the EMRIK 2.5-seat sofa in Bonded Leather! It is made from high-quality cowhide leather in a stylish brown finish that gives it a luxurious feel. With a generous width, a comfortable seat depth and cold foam padding in the seat cushions and backrest, you can sit back and enjoy a wonderful moment with your family and friends. This soffa is available only online
